---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experiments Lab · AI-LAB">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 space-y-10">
    <header class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-900 via-zinc-950 to-black p-10">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-400">AI-LAB EXPERIMENTS</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-black text-white">Experiments Lab</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-lg text-zinc-300">
        Laboratorio de experimentos, benchmarks y validaciones tecnicas del AI-LAB.
        Resultados reales con GPUs AMD, LM Studio y routing cognitivo.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 1</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">LM Studio Multi-Node Routing</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Test de routing distribuido entre RX9070 y RX7900XT con failover automatico. Comparativa de latencia por modelo y nodo.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Routing</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Failover</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400">Pendiente</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 2</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">AMD GPU Telemetry Stack</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Pipeline completo de telemetria: windows_exporter, LibreHWMonitor, PowerShell API, Prometheus scrape y Grafana dashboard.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Telemetria</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Prometheus</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Completado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 3</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">SSE Realtime Runtime Mesh</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Streaming de eventos en vivo via Server-Sent Events. Heartbeat cada 3s, 9 tipos de eventos, buffer de 200 eventos.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">SSE</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Event Bus</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Completado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 4</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">OpenWebUI Multi-Model Orchestration</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Orquestacion de 4 rutas de modelo via Router API desde Open WebUI. Streaming sanitizado y CORS.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Orquestacion</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">CORS</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Completado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 5</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">Cognitive Event Bus & Analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Bus de eventos cognitivos con 9 tipos de evento, agregacion en runtime_analytics, health score y endpoint /api/analytics.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Event Bus</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Analytics</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Completado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Experimento 6</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">Health Scoring AI Runtime</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Sistema de puntuacion de salud 0-100 basado en GPUs online, gateway, router, Prometheus, Docker y latencia.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Health</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Scoring</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400">Completado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
